name: REGISTRATION for BPL III - SEP 29th 2012
description:
Register your team for our second tournament - BPLIII

32 TEAM MAXIMUM SO REGISTER FAST!


        ****29th September 2012 ****


BEER PONG LEAGUES LAST EVER TOURNAMENT!!

Each team registered will consist of a maximum of 2 players.

1st Place - £300
2nd Place - £150
3rd Place - Beer Pong Table OR £50

BEST DRESSED TEAM - WIN TSHIRTS

You will need to arrive at the frog and fiddle in cheltenham at 12:00pm to check your team in and be handed your tournamnet Schedule.

ALL TEAMS MUST REGISTER BY FRIDAY 28TH SEP!


ONCE REGISTERED - WE WILL CONFIRM YOUR TEAM NAME ON ARRIVAL TO THE TOURNAMENT! - 

----------BRING YOUR EMAIL/RECIEPT!---------
